headline: Pinterest Can Still Prosper. Google Search Isn’t a Worry, Analyst Says.
summary: Pinterest  likely will keep on attracting users and increasing its revenue even if search traffic weakens,  J.P. Morgan  says. Anmuth wrote in a research note on Tuesday that he believes Pinterest has done a good job at working towards goals the company laid out for investors in 2023.
